text.section:
No action may be brought against a person, firm, or corporation who furnishes confidential records, reports, statements, notes, or other information to one of the following agencies or their authorized agents, for purposes of research and study:
The Medical and Chirurgical Faculty or its allied committees;
An "in-hospital" staff committee;
A nationally organized medical society or research group;
The State Department of Health and Mental Hygiene; or
The Maryland Institute for Emergency Medical Services Systems.
